subproject.corporate outcome: National and local governments and communities have the capacities to adapt to climate change and make inclusive and sustainable environment & energy decisions benefitting in particular under-served populations
subproject.description: The project aims making necessary improvements in laws, Regulations, norms and standards, in determining per capita waste generation capacity in the country, creation of the National Solid Waste Data Bank, conducting feasibility studies and preparing planning guidelines, and conducting a small-scale solid waste management improvement pilot project in one of the rural areas of the country.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: Solid Waste Management
